# GeoOptimizer - Harita Hive Performance Tool
# Apache 2.0 License
#
# Compresses geospatial datasets without quality loss
# Reduces file sizes by 60-80% using advanced algorithms
#
# Features:
# - Lossless compression for vector and raster data
# - Format-specific optimization algorithms
# - Batch processing with parallel compression
# - Metadata preservation
# - Progressive JPEG compression for rasters
# - Topology-preserving vector simplification
#
# Compression Techniques:
# - LZ4 for fast compression/decompression
# - ZSTD for maximum compression ratio
# - Custom GIS-optimized algorithms
# - Predictive encoding for coordinate data
#
# Typical Results:
# - Shapefiles: 70-85% size reduction
# - GeoTIFF: 60-75% size reduction
# - GeoJSON: 80-90% size reduction
#
# Usage:
# geo-optimizer --input dataset.shp --algorithm zstd --level 9
# geo-optimizer --batch-optimize directory/ --preserve-quality